    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>尽显DIY风格！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219140/extras/77bc391e7faa3821e5e5f97f6e360707.poster.avif?t=1771509193\" width=616 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219140/extras/77bc391e7faa3821e5e5f97f6e360707.webm?t=1771509193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219140/extras/77bc391e7faa3821e5e5f97f6e360707.mp4?t=1771509193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你不需要华丽的马厩或强大的坐骑。你的故事从房间开始：在这里，你可以创造属于自己的马头棒，并规划所有的冒险之旅。展示你赢得的奖杯，从自己温馨的小天地中成为闪耀的马头棒骑士明星。<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>让他们看看你如何在障碍赛道上大显身手。</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219140/extras/811c634ca2edac7232acf4ed2f47b2e1.poster.avif?t=1771509193\" width=616 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219140/extras/811c634ca2edac7232acf4ed2f47b2e1.webm?t=1771509193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219140/extras/811c634ca2edac7232acf4ed2f47b2e1.mp4?t=1771509193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>拿起你的马头棒，在各种场地和路线中展示你的技能——从室内健身房到原始森林地形应有尽有，整个城市都等你去探索。只需打开地图，选择你想去的地方！跑跳越过障碍，提升你的技能，为你和你的马头棒赢得胜利！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>与你的马头棒一起跃向新高度！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219140/extras/2b46821345238f83f99d78eb26ee8243.poster.avif?t=1771509193\" width=616 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219140/extras/2b46821345238f83f99d78eb26ee8243.webm?t=1771509193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219140/extras/2b46821345238f83f99d78eb26ee8243.mp4?t=1771509193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>每个障碍赛道上都有各种增益道具，帮你在骑乘时获得优势。你可以被抛向空中，跳过高得离谱的障碍，或者获得速度加成，迅速通过赛道。根据你的需求选择马头棒——无论你是想提升速度还是跳跃高度，都能找到适合你的马头棒，助你登上领奖台！<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>让你的定制马头棒引领潮流！</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219140/extras/c5636752f256b9c5cccb88c0a63e7642.poster.avif?t=1771509193\" width=616 height=324 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219140/extras/c5636752f256b9c5cccb88c0a63e7642.webm?t=1771509193\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3219140/extras/c5636752f256b9c5cccb88c0a63e7642.mp4?t=1771509193\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>你的马头棒将与你一起经历各种挑战，它也值得与众不同！为你的马头棒进行个性化定制，选择颜色、形状，甚至各种配件，让它在你骑乘时光彩夺目！",
